Nicholas Rodriguez, the artistic 
director of The Broadway Dreams Foundation, discusses The 
Broadway Dreams Foundation and their upcoming "Circle of Dreams 
NYC Showcase." Rodriguez talks with Bloomberg's  Kathleen Hays  
and Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 05:19
 